<svg viewBox="0 0 700 500" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" style="width:100%;height:auto;background:#111113;border-radius:12px;border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.08);margin:20px 0">
  <text x="20" y="28" fill="#fafafa" font-size="15" font-weight="700" font-family="sans-serif">Where DVOL Called It — and Where It Missed</text>
  <text x="20" y="48" fill="#a1a1aa" font-size="13" font-family="sans-serif">What this index actually told you at each key event</text>
  <rect x="20" y="64" width="660" height="70" rx="8" fill="#18181b"/>
  <text x="36" y="90" fill="#fafafa" font-size="14.5" font-weight="700" font-family="sans-serif">March 2020 · COVID Shock</text>
  <text x="36" y="112" fill="#a1a1aa" font-size="13" font-family="sans-serif">Bitcoin's own vol measure exceeded 200% annualized</text>
  <text x="664" y="100" fill="#22c55e" font-size="13.5" font-weight="700" text-anchor="end" font-family="sans-serif">Caught the extreme</text>
  <rect x="20" y="142" width="660" height="70" rx="8" fill="#18181b"/>
  <text x="36" y="168" fill="#fafafa" font-size="14.5" font-weight="700" font-family="sans-serif">November 2022 · FTX Collapse</text>
  <text x="36" y="190" fill="#a1a1aa" font-size="13" font-family="sans-serif">DVOL peaked post-launch high vs. real bottom on 11/21</text>
  <text x="664" y="178" fill="#fbbf24" font-size="13.5" font-weight="700" text-anchor="end" font-family="sans-serif">~10-day lag</text>
  <rect x="20" y="220" width="660" height="70" rx="8" fill="#18181b"/>
  <text x="36" y="246" fill="#fafafa" font-size="14.5" font-weight="700" font-family="sans-serif">Early 2023 · Record Low Vol</text>
  <text x="36" y="268" fill="#a1a1aa" font-size="13" font-family="sans-serif">What followed was an ETF-hope rally, not a crash</text>
  <text x="664" y="256" fill="#60a5fa" font-size="13.5" font-weight="700" text-anchor="end" font-family="sans-serif">No directional signal</text>
  <rect x="20" y="298" width="660" height="70" rx="8" fill="#18181b"/>
  <text x="36" y="324" fill="#fafafa" font-size="14.5" font-weight="700" font-family="sans-serif">January 2024 · Spot ETF Approval</text>
  <text x="36" y="346" fill="#a1a1aa" font-size="13" font-family="sans-serif">Fell 11%+ within weeks (classic sell-the-news)</text>
  <text x="664" y="334" fill="#f7931a" font-size="13.5" font-weight="700" text-anchor="end" font-family="sans-serif">Event premium unwound</text>
  <rect x="20" y="376" width="660" height="70" rx="8" fill="#18181b" stroke="#a78bfa" stroke-width="1.5"/>
  <text x="36" y="402" fill="#fafafa" font-size="14.5" font-weight="700" font-family="sans-serif">2025-2026 · Deribit vs. IBIT Share War</text>
  <text x="36" y="424" fill="#a1a1aa" font-size="13" font-family="sans-serif">Deribit's 90%+ share fell to ~39%, lead changes hands</text>
  <text x="664" y="412" fill="#a78bfa" font-size="13.5" font-weight="700" text-anchor="end" font-family="sans-serif">The benchmark itself split</text>
  <text x="350" y="470" fill="#e4e4e7" font-size="13" font-weight="600" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif">A fear gauge tells you magnitude — not direction, not the exact bottom date</text>
</svg>
</div>
